summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 4.0°C), outside temperature (down 3.6°C), and inside temperature (down 2.1°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 8%) and rainfall (up 2.0 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 615 m) and light levels (up 4467 lux).

The past week and month had observable variation in cloud levels (up 1214 m), light levels (up 6438 lux), outside temperature (up 6.6°C), and feels like temperature (up 8.2°C) when compared to today.
